<HEADLINE>
FT  09 DEC 93 / London Stock Exchange: New highs and lows for 1993
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
NEW HIGHS (287)
BRITISH FUNDS (46) CANADIANS (1) Brascan, BANKS (11) ANZ, Abbey Natl., Bank
of Scotland, Barclays, HSBC, Do. HK, Lloyds, Natl. Westminster, Royal Bank
of Scotland, Standard Chart., TSB, BREWERS (4) Gibbs Mew, Morland, Scott. &amp;
New., Vaux, BLDG MATLS (9) BPB Inds., Baggeridge Brick, Caradon, Do. Pf.,
Meyer, Rugby, Sheffield Ins., Travis Perkins, Wolseley, BUSINESS SERVS (1)
Fact (EW), CHEMS (2) Bayer, Halstead (J), CONGLOMERATES (2) Harrisons &amp;
Crosfield, Hawtin, CONTG &amp; CONSTRCN (3) Banner Homes, Barratt Dev., EBC,
ELECTRICALS (1) BICC Cap. Fin. 10 3/4 pc Bds., ELECTRICITY (16) ELECTRONICS
(1) Druck, ENG GEN (4) BSS, Clyde Blowers, Hampson, Molins, FOOD MANUF (2)
Devro, Nestle, HEALTH &amp; HSEHOLD (1) Amersham, HOTELS &amp; LEIS (3) Castle
Comms., Rank, Do. Pf., INSCE COMPOSITE (1) Allianz, INV TRUSTS (102) MEDIA
(9) Capital Radio, Carlton Comms., Flextech, HTV, Haynes Pub., Reed Intl.,
Sleepy Kids, Southnews, Trinity Intl., MTL &amp; MTL FORMING (3) Castings,
Manganese Bronze, Simsmetal, MISC (5) BAT Inds. 12 1/4 pc Ln. 2003/08,
Birkby, Headlam, Heritage, LGW, MOTORS (5) Caffyns, Dixon, Lex Service,
Lucas, Do. Warrants, OTHER FINCL (2) Natl Home Lns. Pf., Perpetual, OTHER
INDLS (1) Whitecroft, PACKG, PAPER &amp; PRINTG (4) AG, Bemrose, Kymene, Repola,
PROP (8) Clarke Nickolls &amp; Coombs, Evans of Leeds, Frogmore Ests., Greycoat,
Land Secs., MEPC, Slough Ests. Pf., Warner Est., STORES (3) Argos, Cantors,
