<HEADLINE>
FT  09 DEC 93 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
De Beers and Anglos led the market higher, with respective gains of R4 and
R10 to R93.50 and R178, the latter at a new closing high. The overall index
rose 85 to 4,391, while the golds index added 88 at 1,990 and industrials 55
at 5,025.
