FT  09 DEC 93 / UK Company News: IMC exercises its ICD option
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
IMC Industries is exercising its option to subscribe for 6.95m shares at 7p
in International Communication &amp; Data, the marketing services company. The
move has triggered a mandatory 9 1/2 p a share offer for ICD.
