this disposal. Operating profits on continuing operations were Pounds
469,000 (Pounds 33,000 losses), on sales of Pounds 23m (Pounds 21.8m).
Net earnings per share came to 1.17p (1.64p losses), but in the light of the
further improvement required, the interim dividend is again omitted.
