<HEADLINE>
FT  08 DEC 93 / UK Company News: Baring Tribune debenture placing
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Baring Tribune Investment Trust is placing a further Pounds 10m nominal of
9.125 per cent debenture stock 2012.
The stock will be placed on a yield basis, and will form a single series
with the Pounds 15m of the stock currently outstanding.
</TEXT>
